{# EXAMPLE: Diagnosis with Differential Diagnoses #}
{# Supports text-only (from history), single image, or multi-image diagnosis. #}

**TASK:**

{% if images and images|length > 1 %}
Analyze these medical images and provide a diagnostic assessment including:
{% elif images and images|length == 1 %}
Analyze this medical image and provide a diagnostic assessment including:
{% else %}
Based on the clinical information provided, provide a diagnostic assessment including:
{% endif %}

1. Primary diagnosis (most likely condition)
2. Differential diagnoses (alternative possibilities ranked by likelihood)
{% if images and images|length > 0 %}
3. Supporting evidence from the image(s)
{% else %}
3. Supporting evidence from the clinical history
{% endif %}
4. Recommended follow-up studies if needed

{% if clinical_history %}
**CLINICAL HISTORY:** {{ clinical_history }}
{% endif %}

{% if patient_info %}
**PATIENT INFORMATION:** {{ patient_info }}
{% endif %}

{% if images and images|length > 0 %}
**IMAGES:**
{% for img in images %}
- {% if img.label %}{{ img.label }}{% else %}Image {{ loop.index }}{% endif %}: {{ img.width }}x{{ img.height }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

**OUTPUT FORMAT:**

```json
{
  "primary_diagnosis": {
    "condition": "string (diagnosis name)",
    "icd10_code": "string (ICD-10 code if known)",
    "confidence": 0.0-1.0,
{% if images and images|length > 0 %}
    "evidence": ["list of imaging findings supporting this diagnosis"]
{% else %}
    "evidence": ["list of clinical factors supporting this diagnosis"]
{% endif %}
  },
  "differential_diagnoses": [
    {
      "condition": "string",
      "confidence": 0.0-1.0,
      "evidence": ["supporting findings"],
      "distinguishing_features": "string (what would rule this in/out)"
    }
  ],
  "key_findings": [
    {
      "finding": "string",
{% if images and images|length > 0 %}
      "location": "string (anatomical location)",
{% endif %}
      "significance": "string (clinical meaning)"
    }
  ],
  "recommendations": ["list of recommended follow-up actions"],
  "limitations": "string (factors limiting diagnostic confidence)",
  "continue": true/false
}
```

**GUIDELINES:**

- Provide at least 2-3 differential diagnoses when appropriate
{% if images and images|length > 0 %}
- Base confidence scores on the strength of imaging evidence
- Note any imaging artifacts or quality issues that affect interpretation
{% else %}
- Base confidence scores on the specificity of clinical presentation
- Note any missing information that would improve diagnostic accuracy
{% endif %}
- Use medical literature search to verify diagnostic criteria if uncertain
- Consider patient demographics and clinical context if provided
